        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is overspray really that big a deal?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes. The City\u2019s landscape guidance explicitly addresses overspray, runoff, and setback from buildings because those patterns can damage walls and structures."
